<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Maintenance Request Created - PropertyOS</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 30px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #10b981;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #10b981;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 0;
    }
    .content h2 {
      color: #1f2937;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .success-box {
      background-color: #d1fae5;
      border-left: 4px solid #10b981;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .success-box h3 {
      color: #065f46;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .info-box {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      border-left: 4px solid #4f46e5;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .info-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 8px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .info-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .info-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .info-value {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #1f2937;
    }
    .priority {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .priority-high {
      background-color: #fef2f2;
      color: #dc2626;
    }
    .priority-medium {
      background-color: #fef3c7;
      color: #d97706;
    }
    .priority-low {
      background-color: #d1fae5;
      color: #059669;
    }
    .description-box {
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .description-box h4 {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #374151;
    }
    .description-box p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4f46e5;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #4338ca;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 30px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>PropertyOS</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Maintenance Request Created</h2>
      <p>Dear {{userName}},</p>
      <p>Your maintenance request has been successfully submitted. Our team will review it and get back to you shortly.</p>

      <div class="success-box">
        <h3>âœ“ Request Submitted Successfully</h3>
        <p style="margin: 0;">Reference ID: <strong>{{requestId}}</strong></p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="description-box">
        <h4>Request Details:</h4>
        <p>{{requestDescription}}</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="info-box">
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Request Title</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{requestTitle}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Category</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{category}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Priority</span>
          <span class="info-value"><span class="priority priority-{{priority}}">{{priority}}</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Property</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{propertyAddress}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Unit</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{unitNumber}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Submitted Date</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{submittedDate}}</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      {{#if trackingUrl}}
      <a href="{{trackingUrl}}" class="button">Track Request Status</a>
      {{/if}}

      <p>You will receive updates as your request progresses. For urgent matters, please contact our maintenance team directly.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} PropertyOS. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This is an automated email, please do not reply.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>